-- sentiment.fl — AI-powered sentiment analysis
-- Requires: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY environment variable

Let reviews be a list containing
    "This product is absolutely amazing! Best purchase I've ever made.",
    "Terrible quality, broke after one day. Complete waste of money.",
    "It's okay, nothing special but gets the job done.",
    "Exceeded all my expectations. Five stars!".

Output "=== Sentiment Analysis Pipeline ===".
Output "Analyzing reviews...".

For each review in reviews:
    @model(temperature: 0, max_tokens: 60)
    Ask claude to "Classify this review as positive, negative, or neutral. Respond with exactly one word." using text review and call the result review_sentiment.
    Output review_sentiment.
End loop.

Output "Done.".
